node.text: The sea bream looks interesting! And yummy!

#CircuitBreakerSg Day 40! Back to our usual homecooked dinner. Chanced upon one of Masa’s fish recipe that looks pretty simple so gave it a try. Basically just pan fried fish fillet then cooked a buttered soy sauce drizzled over. Ok lah not very fantastic but at least something different! 😂

1. Pan fried sea bream with buttered soy sauce 
2. Stir fry Chinese cabbage with canned braised pork ribs
3. Shi Shen Soup (#四神汤)

#wencookforfamily #may2020 #sgig #sgfoodie #instafood #instadinner #homecooked #twodishesonesoup #fishdishes #masarecipe #comfortfood #stayhomeandcook #sgunited
@cuisineparadiseig they 4 pax plus we 2 pax juz nice leh LOL
wow u prepared a plate of my fav fish for me *^_^* @cuisineparadiseig  come lets share =)
@leeweichoo 20g butter, 2 tbsp light soy sauce, 2 tbsp mirin, 2 tbsp sake
May I ask how to make buttered soy sauce?
The sea bream looks interesting! And yummy!
